      <p class="text-xl text-gray-600 mb-10 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
        Practical insights, tutorials, and analysis on how AI is transforming the
        way we spec, write, test, and maintain code.
      </p>

      <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row justify-center gap-4">
